{"type": "article", "id": 30411, "title": "自行车包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-01T23:05:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 90, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160801215708O8f7w0eij2UuJnLk.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>自行车包装并非只有被丢进垃圾桶的命运，当你看到这个名为 Brum Box 的纸板自行车架时或许会觉得它才是主角产品。在 Toms Grinbergs 和 Aldis Blicsons 联手设计了木制儿童自行车 Brum Brum 之后，他们决定为它打造一个实用而且有趣的外包装。考虑到目标受众是 2 到 6 岁的孩子，设计师们沿着包装画上了小房子和车库的图案。Brum Box 就像是一个手工玩具，只需要简单的折叠，小骑手们就轻松地把它组装起来，还能够为图案添上颜色。这是自行车的<a href=\"http://www.brumbrum.me/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 299 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801220219D2szMRTw4Fab96d8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801220219U0BQJhZPcDbOgYsi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801220220mlevGoU7IMR9wydn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160801220220bdtHCXJvBI3fxKgF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.826250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div>"}